                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/17684</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Special Representative <persName type="from"
                            >Rodgers</persName> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegrams]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Querétaro</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-03-29T19:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 29, 1916, 7 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>12. In reply to Department’s March 28, 6 p.m., use railroads, have had further
                    conference, promised definite final reply to-morrow morning. Believe consent
                    being withheld pending settlement protocol.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Rodgers</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
